## Risk & Mitigation

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|-----------|--------|------------|
| SWR cache becomes stale after mutations | Medium | Low | Call `mutate()` after every POST/PATCH/DELETE; use `revalidateOnFocus` |
| Webhook handler processes events too slowly (>500ms) | Medium | Medium | Return 200 immediately after creating the deployment record; build runs async via queue |
| Concurrent webhook deliveries create duplicate deployments | Medium | High | Deduplicate by delivery ID using a database check before processing |
| Slug collision on project creation | Low | Medium | Generate slug from name, check uniqueness, append random suffix if collision |
| Env var encryption key not available in API routes | Low | High | Validate ENCRYPTION_KEY at startup; error early if missing |
| Large build logs from S3 cause slow page loads | Medium | Medium | Stream logs or paginate; set a max display size with "download full log" fallback |
| ANSI escape codes in build logs cause XSS | Low | High | Use a battle-tested ANSI-to-HTML library (ansi-to-html) that sanitizes output |

